flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("", "928A47174BF738A510B83E86D4396A6A", "A forlorn spirit idling in Oakenbane Keep handed me a letter describing a toy soldier left to him in memoriam by his child. The letters \"AAG\" are scrawled over the letter four times in blood. It must be a reference to the names of some goblins around here.")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D0A4E1164EBDAA23EAEDEEA3A8C8AD72", "Deliver the toy to the Forgotten Soldier\'s memorial site.")
calloutDescription: NSLOCTEXT("", "497F8AA34DC81115146171958B3134EB", "Some form of spirit idles nearby bedecked in ancient Aelan armor. It beckons me over.")
name: SQ_RVR_0005_Aagravations
